  "text": "In the following σ B denotes the expression for σ app from Bertulani et al. [CITATION_1] Eq. 5] and σ W/A the result given by Winther and Alder [CITATION_2] . For a given multipolariy λ these two expressions for the CE cross section differ explicitly only in the expressions containing the modified Bessel functions K n and we will consider the ratio of the two expressions leaving out explicit common pre-factors. In particular for the E2 case:",
